{"tid":2163137,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全民驗病毒技術面臨禁制  檢測龍頭告華大侵權","createTime":"2020-08-18T13:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T07:13:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"443275e9a468a38c63a4777b64083c9d95cafd67","tid":2163137,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:11:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/22YRG4JKZJFFDOEGUVYVY7D4KU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2F22YRG4JKZJFFDOEGUVYVY7D4KU%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5mL0CtalYwMF7My3GtbBKd0%3D&h=588e4188\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200818%2F22YRG4JKZJFFDOEGUVYVY7D4KU%2F&h=7be347d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200818/22YRG4JKZJFFDOEGUVYVY7D4KU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n全民驗病毒技術面臨禁制 <br />\n檢測龍頭告華大侵權<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：18區採樣 延至8.31展開<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】獲港府欽點推行全民自願性病毒檢測的華大基因，日前遭專門研發及生產基因組測序儀、佔全球七成市場的龍頭跨國公司入稟本港高等法院，指華大及其相關公司推出的基因測序試劑套裝侵犯其香港註冊的專利。原告要求法庭頒下禁制令，禁止華大供應和銷售該些侵權套裝、銷毀所有存貨，及向原告賠償，案件已排期本月20日處理。雖然華大回應稱本港的病毒檢測均未使用涉案裝備，但有專家指使用的技術「其實係同一樣嘢嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xFINCzQEAYUIjOlrn_cfFHBvWDE=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AGTE4QE56JG2NCTPU7E7XG4MVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxFINCzQEAYUIjOlrn_cfFHBvWDE%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAGTE4QE56JG2NCTPU7E7XG4MVA.jpg&h=f41b34da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■華大基因遭跨國公司ILLUMINA入稟控告侵犯其香港註冊的專利。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。此訴訟涉及到的任何試劑及裝備。中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌則稱，所有病毒檢測均需使用基因測序技術，「其實係同一樣嘢嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促交代銷售對象已獲利益<br />\n<br />\n原告為ILLUMINA CAMBRIDGE LIMITED，六名被告為深圳華大智造科技股份有限公司、香港華大基因醫療設備有限公司、MGI INTERNATIONAL SALES CO LIMITED、華大基因香港研發中心有限公司、香港華大基因科技服務有限公司以及華大基因健康科技（香港）有限公司。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。被告須在命令頒佈後七天內撤回任何侵權的宣傳產品，及14天內將侵權產品交出並由原告銷毀。被告亦須向原告交代侵權產品的銷售對象、及已獲利益等資料，並且就原告的損失作出賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外地判決或影響本港訴訟<br />\n<br />\nILLUMINA早前已在歐美起訴華大侵犯專利，牽涉本港案件中的產品。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本案入稟狀要求被告銷毀侵犯專利的測序工具。大律師解釋，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCIP47/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6ci8LjEs6Y3K7_lGtpO1jZ_QYQA=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3NNE75SDLVC7BO63EKNYXVTUZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6ci8LjEs6Y3K7_lGtpO1jZ_QYQA%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3NNE75SDLVC7BO63EKNYXVTUZI.jpg&h=352b32c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■華大旗下華昇診斷中心已在西環中山紀念公園體育館設立16個「氣膜實驗室」做檢測。資料圖片"},{"pid":"23c47f95ff84d5ea336b9eca63133b4c1da277ae","tid":2163137,"uid":262146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"cfec5699497a67bf017508c68dbee6bec3217a3c","tid":2163137,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"b799337df99ff7afcc71fc2b89871763b9366d5e","tid":2163137,"uid":650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T07:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}